Supplementary Notebook 3B-1¶

PAGA analysis performed on a popular mouse hematopoiesis dataset (Paul et al., 2015)¶

This dataset is shown in Figure 3B of the manuscript.

Tracing myeloid and erythroid differentiation for data of Paul et al. (2015).

saved .h5ad file can be downloaded here

Depending on the desired annotations and genes to be visualized by the user, the following command can be executed to create singlecellVR-compatible .JSON object.

scvr -f file.h5ad -t PAGA -a ANNOTATIONS [-g GENES] [-o OUTPUT]
